abstract: Ignacio 'Nacho' María González Gatti (Spanish pronunciation: [iɣˈna.sjo maˈɾi.a ɣonˈsa.les]; born 14 May 1982) is an Uruguayan professional footballer who plays for Club Nacional de Football as a midfielder.
